        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "WAN 2.2 videos generate natively at 16fps (or at least that's what I gen at). Your video needs to be interpolated up to 24fps to get audio working through MMAudio. I use the node below because it allows for fractional multiples of fps (16->24 instead of a clean 2x interpolation of 16 -> 32). You can also use other interpolation nodes or Topaz if you'd like."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
